title: "RAK-CYB-2026-001: Anatomy of a Sophisticated Android RAT Campaign — DSU/GSI Multi-Environment Infrastructure, Baseband Diagnostic Exploitation, and Cross-Border C2"
version: 1.0.0
date-released: 2026-06-09
